# ACL STANDARD

## Créer

```bash
access-list 1 deny host 172.16.1.10
access-list 1 permit any
```

## Appliquer

```bash
interface fa0/0
ip access-group 1 in
```

ou

```bash
interface fa0/0
ip access-group 1 out
```

## Supprimer

```bash
no access-list 1
```

