# ACL ÉTENDUE

## HTTP + HTTPS uniquement

```bash
access-list 100 permit tcp any host 192.168.1.10 eq 80
access-list 100 permit tcp any host 192.168.1.10 eq 443
access-list 100 deny ip any any
```

## Bloquer SSH

```bash
access-list 100 deny tcp any host 192.168.1.10 eq 22
```

## Bloquer Ping

```bash
access-list 100 deny icmp any any
```

## Autoriser Ping

```bash
access-list 100 permit icmp any any
```

## Appliquer

```bash
interface fa0/0
ip access-group 100 in
```

---

# ACL NOMMÉE

## Création

```bash
ip access-list extended web

deny icmp host 192.168.1.10 host 192.168.100.2

permit tcp host 192.168.1.10 host 192.168.100.2 eq 80

permit tcp host 192.168.1.10 host 192.168.100.2 eq 443

permit ip host 192.168.1.10 host 172.16.1.10

permit ip host 192.168.1.20 host 172.16.1.20

exit
```

## Application

```bash
interface fa0/0
ip access-group web in
```

